---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Blog | Reflections">
    <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div style="width: 100%; height: 400px; background: #ccc; margin-bottom: 40px;">
             <img src="/Arze_K/blog-header.jpg" alt="Home and Family" style="width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover;" />
        </div>
        
        <h1 style="font-size: 3.5rem; text-align: center;">A Season of Gratitude</h1>
        <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 2px; font-weight: 600;">BY KAREN ARZE</div>
        
        <div style="font-size: 1.3rem; line-height: 2; color: #444; first-letter: { font-size: 3rem; color: var(--navy); }">
            <p>
                I am so grateful for the blessings I have been given in this lifetime. Both my children are about to graduate, I'm finally a homeowner <strong>[Yay!]</strong>, and ***** Eye Care has provided me the perfect environment and tools needed to become an even better version of myself.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top: 60px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 30px; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
            <p style="font-style: italic;">Share the warmth:</p>
            <div>
                <button style="background: var(--navy); color: white; border: none; padding: 10px 25px; cursor: pointer; font-family: 'Montserrat';">Leave a Heart ❤️</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</MainLayout>
